1. *Zapad* je poznat po svojim prelepim zalascima sunca. (The *west* is known for its beautiful sunsets.)
2. Mnogi ljudi žele da se presele na *zapad* zbog boljih ekonomskih prilika. (Many people want to move to the *west* for better economic opportunities.)
3. Ovaj grad se nalazi na *zapadnoj* obali reke Dunav. (This city is located on the *western* bank of the Danube River.)
4. *Zapadni* deo grada je poznat po svojim luksuznim restoranima i tržnim centrima. (The *western* part of the city is known for its luxurious restaurants and shopping centers.)
5. *Zapad* Evrope ima dugu istoriju umetnosti i kulture. (The *west* of Europe has a long history of art and culture.)
6. Ova zgrada ima predivan pogled na *zapadni* deo grada. (This building has a beautiful view of the *western* part of the city.)
7. Zadnji voz za *zapad* polazi u 20h. (The last train to the *west* departs at 8 PM.)
8. *Zapadno* društvo ima drugačiju kulturu od istočnog društva. (Western society has a different culture from Eastern society.)
9. Ova planina se nalazi na *zapadu* Srbije. (This mountain is located in the *west* of Serbia.)
10. *Zapadni* Balkan je poznat po svojim prelepim pejzažima i netaknutoj prirodi. (The *western* Balkans are known for their beautiful landscapes and unspoiled nature.)